<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Educator Application Received - MEDH</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family:
          -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto,
          "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f8fafc;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ed8936 0%, #dd6b20 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .header-subtitle {
        font-size: 16px;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }

      .greeting {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2d3748;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .application-details {
        background-color: #fffaf0;
        border: 1px solid #fbd38d;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 25px 0;
      }

      .detail-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 8px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #fbd38d;
      }

      .detail-row:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .detail-label {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #c05621;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .detail-value {
        color: #2d3748;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .application-id {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ed8936 0%, #dd6b20 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 3px 10px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .process-timeline {
        margin: 30px 0;
      }

      .timeline-title {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2d3748;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .timeline-steps {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .timeline-step {
        padding: 12px 0;
        border-left: 3px solid #fbd38d;
        padding-left: 20px;
        margin-left: 10px;
        position: relative;
      }

      .timeline-step:before {
        content: "";
        width: 12px;
        height: 12px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: #ed8936;
        position: absolute;
        left: -7px;
        top: 16px;
      }

      .step-title {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2d3748;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .step-description {
        color: #4a5568;
        font-size: 13px;
        margin-top: 4px;
      }

      .contact-info {
        background-color: #fef5e7;
        border-left: 4px solid #ed8936;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        margin: 25px 0;
      }

      .contact-title {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2d3748;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #2d3748;
        color: #a0aec0;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .footer-logo {
        color: white;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .footer-links {
        margin: 15px 0;
      }

      .footer-links a {
        color: #ed8936;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 0 10px;
      }

      .footer-links a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .disclaimer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #718096;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .email-container {
          margin: 0;
          border-radius: 0;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 30px 20px;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 25px 20px;
        }

        .detail-row {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
          gap: 5px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">🎓 MEDH</div>
        <div class="header-subtitle">Educator Portal</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="content">
        <div class="greeting">
          Dear
          {{name}},
        </div>

        <p>Thank you for submitting your application to join our teaching team
          at MEDH! We greatly appreciate your interest in bringing your
          educational expertise to our skill development platform and
          contributing to our mission of transforming learning experiences.</p>

        <!-- Application Details -->
        <div class="application-details">
          <div class="detail-row">
            <div class="detail-label">Application ID:</div>
            <div class="detail-value">
              <span class="application-id">{{application_id}}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <div class="detail-label">Teaching Mode:</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{teaching_mode}}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <div class="detail-label">Subject Areas:</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{subject_areas}}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <div class="detail-label">Application Date:</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{formatDate
                submitted_at
                "MMMM DD, YYYY"
              }}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <div class="detail-label">Status:</div>
            <div class="detail-value">Under Review</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Your Application ID: {{application_id}}</strong></p>

        <p>We have successfully received your educator application and are
          excited to review your qualifications, teaching experience, and
          educational philosophy. Our talent acquisition team is committed to a
          thoughtful selection process that identifies educators who share our
          passion for innovative, impact-driven instruction.</p>

        <!-- Process Timeline -->
        <div class="process-timeline">
          <div class="timeline-title">📚 Here's what you can expect in the
            coming weeks:</div>
          <ul class="timeline-steps">
            <li class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-title">Application Review (2-3 days)</div>
              <div class="step-description">Our academic team will evaluate your
                credentials, experience, and teaching philosophy</div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-title">Teaching Demonstration (if selected)</div>
              <div class="step-description">A brief online session where you'll
                showcase your teaching style in your area of expertise (15-20
                minutes)</div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-title">Faculty Interview (shortlisted candidates)</div>
              <div class="step-description">A conversation with our academic
                leadership team to discuss educational approaches and alignment
                with MEDH's vision</div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-title">Final Selection</div>
              <div class="step-description">Offer extended to selected educators</div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>We aim to complete the initial review within
          <strong>10 business days</strong>
          of your application submission. Candidates advancing to the teaching
          demonstration phase will be contacted with scheduling options and
          demonstration guidelines.</p>

        <p>At MEDH, we believe educators are catalysts for transformation. Our
          platform empowers instructors to focus on what they do best—inspiring
          and guiding learners while providing the technological infrastructure
          and pedagogical support to maximize impact.</p>

        <div class="contact-info">
          <div class="contact-title">🎯 Educator Recruitment</div>
          <p>If you have any questions about your application or our selection
            process, please contact our Educator Success team:</p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> teach@medh.co</p>
          <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +91 77108 40696</p>
          <p><strong>Please reference your application ID:
              {{application_id}}
              in all communications.</strong></p>
        </div>

        <p>We appreciate your patience during our selection process and look
          forward to potentially welcoming you to our community of passionate
          educators who are shaping the future of skills education.</p>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
          <strong>Warm regards,</strong><br />
          Academic Talent Team<br />
          <strong>MEDH Learning Platform</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        <div class="footer-logo">MEDH</div>
        <div>Empowering educators to transform lives through learning</div>

        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="https://www.medh.co/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>
          |
          <a href="https://www.medh.co/terms-of-service">Terms of Service</a>
          |
          <a href="mailto:teach@medh.co">Contact Educators</a>
        </div>

        <div class="disclaimer">
          <p>&copy;
            {{currentYear}}
            MEDH Learning Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 10px;">This email confirms receipt of your
            application. Our team will be in touch within 2 business days to
            discuss next steps.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
            <strong>MEDH Learning Platform</strong><br />
            📧 teach@medh.co | 📞 +91 77108 40696<br />
            🌐
            <a
              href="https://www.medh.co"
              style="color: #ed8936;"
            >www.medh.co</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>